divs: sighting detailsi received a call from my father who said there had been a plane crash in wenona md, there were 911 reports calls from residents reporting a plane crash, local news stated that 911 was dispatched but local coast guard refused to dispatch helicopters due to wether conditions (it was raining). i have relatives who live near the water and they state that they did hear the sounds of a motor that seemed to sputter and then a large crash and splach into the water. no debris has been found. no evidence of a crash of any sort or a plane crash has been found as of 1430 1\22\12. the community is talking about the fact that many people heard this event yet nothing has been found.
